<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Han har makt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Han har makt, Han har makt.
 Han er oppstått fra de døde,
 Han har makt.
 Hvert ett kne skal seg bøye,
 hver en tunge skal bekjenne;
 at Jesus Herre er.

[V2]
 He is Lord, He is Lord,
 He has risen from the dead
 And He is Lord,
 Every knee shall bow,
 Every tongue confess,
 That Jesus Christ is Lord

[V3]
 He's my Lord, He's my Lord,
 He has risen from the dead
 And He's my Lord,
 Every knee shall bow,
 Every tongue confess,
 That Jesus Christ is Lord</lyrics>
<aka>He is Lord</aka>
